# Claude Code indexing exclusions (see AGENTS.md section 9).
# Aligns with .cursorignore where possible. Narrow .cursor log patterns keep logs out of default
# context but still allow reading them via explicit path, open file, or paste.

# From .gitignore + dependency/build/lock/log exclusions
# (node_modules etc. are ignored by default; reference explicitly when needed.)

*.db
.DS_Store
.aider*
.claude/
Thumbs.db
dist/
dist-electron/
node_modules/
release/
test-results/

# Dependency and build artifacts
coverage/
.next/

# Lock files and large non-source files
package-lock.json

# Local Cursor debug logs only (replaces blanket .cursor/ and global *.log so repo/app logs stay available)
.cursor/*.log
